desc:#SD Algo IIRF (Lowpass)

// https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HexzW0EZal8
// Inifinite Impulse Response filter (IIRF)

@sample
average = (spl0 + previous) / 2;
previous = spl0;
spl0 = spl1 = average;

